{
  "page": "Solar",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>A <b>solar</b> refers to a loft, upper room, or upper part of a medieval house, often used as the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lord</a>'s private chamber.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Solars_in_Westeros\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Solars in Westeros</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Solars_in_Westeros\">Solars in Westeros</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Solar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Solars in Westeros\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Many castles and towers in <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> have a solar. These include:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Ashford\" title=\"Ashford\">Ashford</a> Castle<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a>\n<ul><li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander%27s_Tower\" title=\"Lord Commander&#39;s Tower\">Lord Commander's Tower</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Tower\" title=\"King&#39;s Tower\">King's Tower</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The armory<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Gates_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Gates of the Moon\">Gates of the Moon</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwow.5B.5Balayne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Calayne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwow.5B.5Balayne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Calayne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Griffin%27s_Roost\" title=\"Griffin&#39;s Roost\">Griffin's Roost</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a> (a spare drafty room as large as the halls of many smaller castles)<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Raventree_Hall\" title=\"Raventree Hall\">Raventree Hall</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a>:\n<ul><li>In the king's apartments in <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor%27s_Holdfast\" title=\"Maegor&#39;s Holdfast\">Maegor's Holdfast</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>In the queen's apartments in Maegor's Holdfast<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>In the <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_the_Hand\" title=\"Tower of the Hand\">Tower of the Hand</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Below the <a href=\"/index.php/Rookery\" title=\"Rookery\">rookery</a>, in the <a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a>'s chambers<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a>'s chambers in the Kitchen Keep<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_15-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-15\">&#91;15&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> (three-sided, like the castle itself)<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_16-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-16\">&#91;16&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Pyke\" title=\"Pyke\">Pyke</a> (damp and drafty)<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_17-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-17\">&#91;17&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_18-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-18\">&#91;18&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Standfast\" title=\"Standfast\">Standfast</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_19-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-19\">&#91;19&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_20-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-20\">&#91;20&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_21-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-21\">&#91;21&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Solar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Wedding\" title=\"Golden Wedding\">Golden Wedding</a>, the young <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a> granted audience to any lord or knight who wished a private word with him, agreeing to speak with them in his solar.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_22-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-22\">&#91;22&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_78_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">78&#160;AC</a>, King Jaehaerys I summoned his son, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Vaegon_Targaryen\" title=\"Vaegon Targaryen\">Vaegon Targaryen</a>, in his solar and announced him he was sent to the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_23-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-23\">&#91;23&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a> used to supper in the tranquility of his solar with his wife, Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Daenaera_Velaryon\" title=\"Daenaera Velaryon\">Daenaera Velaryon</a>, and his friend, <a href=\"/index.php/Gaemon_Palehair\" title=\"Gaemon Palehair\">Gaemon Palehair</a>. It was during one of these meal that Gaemon a was <a href=\"/index.php/Poison\" title=\"Poison\">poisoned</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_24-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-24\">&#91;24&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Solar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Solar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> and his daughters <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a> usually eat meals in the solar of the <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_the_Hand\" title=\"Tower of the Hand\">Tower of the Hand</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Wight\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wight\">wight</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Othor\" title=\"Othor\">Othor</a> attacks <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Night&#39;s Watch\">Lord Commander of the Night's Watch</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Jeor_Mormont\" title=\"Jeor Mormont\">Jeor Mormont</a> in his solar, but <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> defeats it by setting it and the room on fire.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Solar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Acting <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> frequently does business in the solar of the Tower of the Hand.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_25-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-25\">&#91;25&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Solar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> has come to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> and taken up the position of Hand of the King, and Tyrion is reluctant to consider the Hand's solar as no longer his.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_26-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-26\">&#91;26&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Jon Snow is accused of treachery by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Alliser_Thorne\" title=\"Alliser Thorne\">Alliser Thorne</a> in the solar in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Tower\" title=\"King&#39;s Tower\">King's Tower</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_27-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-27\">&#91;27&#93;</a></sup> Later, <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a> demonstrates the fiery glow of <a href=\"/index.php/Lightbringer\" title=\"Lightbringer\">Lightbringer</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Aemon\">Aemon</a> in that solar, radiance filling the room.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_28-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-28\">&#91;28&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Solar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a> meets with <a href=\"/index.php/Nestor_Royce\" title=\"Nestor Royce\">Nestor Royce</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Lords_Declarant\" title=\"Lords Declarant\">Lords Declarant</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>'s solar.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_29-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-29\">&#91;29&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_30-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-30\">&#91;30&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Solar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>This was <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">my father's</a> solar. He ruled the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> from here, wisely and well. He liked to sit beside that window. The light was good there, and whenever he looked up from his work he could see the <a href=\"/index.php/Trident\" title=\"Trident\">river</a>. When his eyes were tired he would have <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Cat</a> read to him. <a href=\"/index.php/Littlefinger\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Littlefinger\">Littlefinger</a> and I built a castle out of wooden blocks once, there beside the door. You will never know how sick it makes me to see you in this room, <a href=\"/index.php/Kingslayer\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kingslayer\">Kingslayer</a>. You will never know how much I despise you.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_31-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-31\">&#91;31&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Solar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Wikipedia: <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Solar_(room)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Solar (room)\">Solar (room)</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight\" title=\"The Hedge Knight\">The Hedge Knight</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_52\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 52\">Chapter 52</a>, Jon VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_6\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 6\">Chapter 6</a>, Jon I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_5\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 5\">Chapter 5</a>, Samwell I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_34\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 34\">Chapter 34</a>, Catelyn VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwow.5B.5Balayne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Calayne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink